org.openimaj.image.processing.face.tracking.clm

Class MultiTracker.TrackedFace

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.openimaj.image.processing.face.detection.DetectedFace
      • org.openimaj.image.processing.face.tracking.clm.MultiTracker.TrackedFace
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ReadableBinary, ReadWriteableBinary, WriteableBinary
    Enclosing class:
    MultiTracker

    public static class MultiTracker.TrackedFace
extends DetectedFace
    Encapsulates the variables for a single tracked face. This includes the model, the shape parameters, the last-matched template and the bounding rectangle.
    Version:
    $Author$, $Revision$, $Date$
    Author:
    David Dupplaw (dpd@ecs.soton.ac.uk)
    Created:
    4 Jul 2012
